{"title":"如何Vibe Coding弥散渐变？","slug":"ig271zxza8ge9xpb","summary":"所谓的“弥散渐变”（也叫 Mesh Gradient, Aura Gradient, 或毛玻璃渐变），是目前 UI 设计中最能体现“高级感”和“氛围感”的手法之一。它的核心特点是 色彩之间没有清晰的界限，像烟雾一样柔和地融合在一起 。 在 Vibe Coding（用 AI 辅助编","category":"Vibe Coding技巧","tags":["PART1️⃣ AI设计工作流&Vibe Coding","Vibe Coding技巧"],"featured":false,"order":34,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2026-01-25","wordCount":1867,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/ig271zxza8ge9xpb","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"u8900a3b4\" id=\"u8900a3b4\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc0534ab1\" id=\"uc0534ab1\">所谓的“弥散渐变”（也叫 Mesh Gradient, Aura Gradient, 或毛玻璃渐变），是目前 UI 设计中最能体现“高级感”和“氛围感”的手法之一。它的核心特点是</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub6ffa888\" id=\"ub6ffa888\">色彩之间没有清晰的界限，像烟雾一样柔和地融合在一起</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5b81a90d\" id=\"u5b81a90d\">。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u023e6f0e\" id=\"u023e6f0e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4501a48b\" id=\"u4501a48b\">在 Vibe Coding（用 AI 辅助编程）的语境下，手写复杂的 CSS </span><code data-lake-id=\"u37bc0a2e\" id=\"u37bc0a2e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub6488bb0\" id=\"ub6488bb0\">radial-gradient</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0dd77e16\" id=\"u0dd77e16\"> 或者 SVG </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud01ce0f1\" id=\"ud01ce0f1\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub5cfe96b\" id=\"ub5cfe96b\">feGaussianBlur</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9c66c155\" id=\"u9c66c155\"> 是非常痛苦且低效的。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub1380bc8\" id=\"ub1380bc8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u58d152e0\" id=\"u58d152e0\">我们要利用 AI 懂语义的优势，用“描述”来生成这种效果。下面我将从原理到实操，教你如何用 Vibe Coding 的方式实现弥散渐变。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22GqprG%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"cbc0015b\" id=\"cbc0015b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8e23842d\" id=\"u8e23842d\">核心原理：解构“弥散”</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u56b6fb81\" id=\"u56b6fb81\"><span data-lake-id=\"u22fb4ef8\" id=\"u22fb4ef8\">在告诉 AI 怎么做之前，你需要知道它底层的实现逻辑。弥散渐变通常不是一个单一的背景属性，而是由两个核心要素组成的“障眼法”：</span></p><ol list=\"ud1d39e87\"><li fid=\"u4b820899\" data-lake-id=\"u07953603\" id=\"u07953603\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud4121353\" id=\"ud4121353\">色块 (Color Blobs)：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5ef714ea\" id=\"u5ef714ea\"> 几个颜色不同、位置重叠的圆形或不规则形状。</span></li><li fid=\"u4b820899\" data-lake-id=\"u993743e6\" id=\"u993743e6\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u24794cd7\" id=\"u24794cd7\">极致模糊 (Extreme Blur)：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u64eead98\" id=\"u64eead98\"> 给这些色块加上巨大的高斯模糊滤镜，让它们化开。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"u059f454d\" id=\"u059f454d\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5189feb4\" id=\"u5189feb4\">Vibe Coding 的策略就是：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u77a24e2b\" id=\"u77a24e2b\"> 指挥 AI 生成这几个色块，然后让 AI 把它们“糊”掉，最后放到背景层。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uff1c68f1\" id=\"uff1c68f1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u272dbc8d\" id=\"u272dbc8d\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"uaf040c26\" id=\"uaf040c26\"><span data-lake-id=\"u48d18f79\" id=\"u48d18f79\">我将目前最流行的弥散渐变分为四大类，并为你提供每一类的 Vibe Coding 指南。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22XMKav%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"8e9d29e9\" id=\"8e9d29e9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0feb6336\" id=\"u0feb6336\">Vibe Coding 弥散渐变的万能公式 (复习一下)</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ufa85a8aa\" id=\"ufa85a8aa\"><span data-lake-id=\"u10263c79\" id=\"u10263c79\">无论哪种类型，AI 实现弥散渐变最稳定、最可控的方法依然是**“叠加法 + 极致模糊”**。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2232a5e8\" id=\"u2232a5e8\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u411b4c66\" id=\"u411b4c66\">核心逻辑 = [定位] + [形状/色块] + [极致模糊]</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6297fc98\" id=\"u6297fc98\"><span data-lake-id=\"uacd3c5e2\" id=\"uacd3c5e2\">记住这个逻辑，我们来看不同类型的变体。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22zbgfx%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"20663247\" id=\"20663247\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9096b29a\" id=\"u9096b29a\">类型一：氛围感大背景 (The Atmospheric Background)</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u8aa64435\" id=\"u8aa64435\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9edea946\" id=\"u9edea946\">这是最常见的一种。几个巨大的、柔和的色块在背景中若隐若现，营造出一种梦幻、高级的基调。它们通常没有明确的形状，色彩相互融合。</span></p><ul list=\"u492aca20\"><li fid=\"uad82e9a2\" data-lake-id=\"ued964b8c\" id=\"ued964b8c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4d6b5092\" id=\"u4d6b5092\">视觉特征：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1f15fe13\" id=\"u1f15fe13\"> 覆盖全屏、颜色柔和 pastel、边界极其模糊、位置随机。</span></li><li fid=\"uad82e9a2\" data-lake-id=\"u1c72b5fc\" id=\"u1c72b5fc\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubc318a27\" id=\"ubc318a27\">适用场景：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u112c7fe8\" id=\"u112c7fe8\"> SaaS 产品官网首页、登录页、Hero Section。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id=\"12839643\" id=\"12839643\"><span data-lake-id=\"u91c0808e\" id=\"u91c0808e\">Vibe Coding 指南：</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"ud37b503d\" id=\"ud37b503d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u74119bf0\" id=\"u74119bf0\">这个类型的关键是“大”</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4df9474d\" id=\"u4df9474d\">和</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u04b38ec6\" id=\"u04b38ec6\">“乱”（随机感）。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4a952ed2\" id=\"u4a952ed2\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf7eb8951\" id=\"uf7eb8951\">Prompt 策略：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua85b4380\" id=\"ua85b4380\"> 你需要告诉 AI 创建几个“巨大的、漂浮的球体”，并把它们放在内容后面“糊掉”。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucb3a30b7\" id=\"ucb3a30b7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2c98c73b\" id=\"u2c98c73b\">实操 Vibe Prompt (发给 Cursor/v0):</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua8ccf15d\" id=\"ua8ccf15d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u309b2fe6\" id=\"u309b2fe6\">&quot;I need a dreamy, atmospheric background for this landing page.</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u15288fa5\" id=\"u15288fa5\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6e16ffb6\" id=\"u6e16ffb6\">Implementation:</span></strong></p><ol list=\"u8ab9dfb0\"><li fid=\"u04e714a8\" data-lake-id=\"u415d28ec\" id=\"u415d28ec\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8be9a19e\" id=\"u8be9a19e\">Create a fixed background container (</span><code data-lake-id=\"uf76ff2cf\" id=\"uf76ff2cf\"><span data-lake-id=\"u27a7ada4\" id=\"u27a7ada4\">fixed inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u91280d2c\" id=\"u91280d2c\">).</span></li><li fid=\"u04e714a8\" data-lake-id=\"ucfdd2a98\" id=\"ucfdd2a98\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5a4c0361\" id=\"u5a4c0361\">Inside it, place 3-4 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u69bbc165\" id=\"u69bbc165\">massive</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u72bca22c\" id=\"u72bca22c\"> randomly positioned colored blobs (circles). Use soft, pastel colors like muted blue, purple, and peach.</span></li><li fid=\"u04e714a8\" data-lake-id=\"u804329a3\" id=\"u804329a3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7e39ad98\" id=\"u7e39ad98\">Apply </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u87d9349c\" id=\"u87d9349c\">extreme</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue70a3dd5\" id=\"ue70a3dd5\"> blur to these blobs (try </span><code data-lake-id=\"uc1a92cf0\" id=\"uc1a92cf0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u849f2409\" id=\"u849f2409\">blur-[150px]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u2a519b75\" id=\"u2a519b75\"> or more) and reduce opacity so they blend seamlessly into a soft haze.</span></li><li fid=\"u04e714a8\" data-lake-id=\"u392606d3\" id=\"u392606d3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u490952d7\" id=\"u490952d7\">Ensure the site content is readable on top.&quot;</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"u9f517f1e\" id=\"u9f517f1e\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub345e42c\" id=\"ub345e42c\">设计师暗语（Vibe Check）：</span></strong></p><ul list=\"ub135e2e6\"><li fid=\"ud5ea888e\" data-lake-id=\"u7341191f\" id=\"u7341191f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u29ce0e4f\" id=\"u29ce0e4f\">如果 AI 做出来太清晰，就喊：&quot;Too sharp! Make it softer, more diffused.&quot; (太锐利了，糊一点)</span></li><li fid=\"ud5ea888e\" data-lake-id=\"u2e732c53\" id=\"u2e732c53\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua29f2858\" id=\"ua29f2858\">如果颜色太脏，就喊：&quot;Use cleaner, brighter pastel colors.&quot; (用干净点的粉彩色)</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u3ccb8986\" id=\"u3ccb8986\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1769333090493-ed68c172-ae89-4fab-a5d8-d903d00294f7.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ucd60f39a-b6d8-4adc-a0b8-57ea3cd319c%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uf66420f0-73bc-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A1099%2C%22height%22%3A646%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2026-01-25%2017.24.31.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A2247876%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A2198%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1292%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22AURA%20TESTIMONIALS%20PRICING%20FEATURES%20GET%20STARTED%20DESIGN%20THAT%20FEELS%20LIK%20LIKE%20A%20BREATH%20OF%20FRESH%20AIR%20CREATE%20STUNNING%2C%20ATMOSPHERIC%20DIGITAL%20EXPERIENCES%20WITH%20OUR%20SET%20OF%20DREAMY%20COMPONENTS.%20FOCUS%20ON%20YOUR%20CONTENT%20WHILE%20WE%20HANDLE%20THE%20AMBIANCE.%20START%20BUILDING%20VIEW%20DEMO%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A145%2C%22y%22%3A64%2C%22width%22%3A95%2C%22height%22%3A39%2C%22text%22%3A%22AURA%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1038%2C%22y%22%3A67%2C%22width%22%3A167%2C%22height%22%3A30%2C%22text%22%3A%22TESTIMONIALS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1312%2C%22y%22%3A67%2C%22width%22%3A98%2C%22height%22%3A32%2C%22text%22%3A%22PRICING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A810%2C%22y%22%3A68%2C%22width%22%3A121%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22FEATURES%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1943%2C%22y%22%3A68%2C%22width%22%3A152%2C%22height%22%3A27%2C%22text%22%3A%22GET%20STARTED%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A406%2C%22y%22%3A325%2C%22width%22%3A1205%2C%22height%22%3A138%2C%22text%22%3A%22DESIGN%20THAT%20FEELS%20LIK%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1524%2C%22y%22%3A325%2C%22width%22%3A278%2C%22height%22%3A137%2C%22text%22%3A%22LIKE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A453%2C%22y%22%3A490%2C%22width%22%3A1299%2C%22height%22%3A132%2C%22text%22%3A%22A%20BREATH%20OF%20FRESH%20AIR%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A418%2C%22y%22%3A696%2C%22width%22%3A1365%2C%22height%22%3A46%2C%22text%22%3A%22CREATE%20STUNNING%2C%20ATMOSPHERIC%20DIGITAL%20EXPERIENCES%20WITH%20OUR%20SET%20OF%20DREAMY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A465%2C%22y%22%3A757%2C%22width%22%3A1271%2C%22height%22%3A42%2C%22text%22%3A%22COMPONENTS.%20FOCUS%20ON%20YOUR%20CONTENT%20WHILE%20WE%20HANDLE%20THE%20AMBIANCE.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A783%2C%22y%22%3A926%2C%22width%22%3A233%2C%22height%22%3A39%2C%22text%22%3A%22START%20BUILDING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1202%2C%22y%22%3A928%2C%22width%22%3A194%2C%22height%22%3A32%2C%22text%22%3A%22VIEW%20DEMO%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23dfe2e9%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ud0d312e2%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u97b0156e\" id=\"u97b0156e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub79ce115\" id=\"ub79ce115\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4699d08b\" id=\"u4699d08b\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf9508791\" id=\"uf9508791\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud1114562\" id=\"ud1114562\"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"ba9a9b73\" id=\"ba9a9b73\"><span data-lake-id=\"u07843604\" id=\"u07843604\">类型二：极光流体 (The Aurora Flow)</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u22f10a16\" id=\"u22f10a16\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud05b27af\" id=\"ud05b27af\">这种类型的渐变不是块状的，而是呈现出一种</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1dcd5a25\" id=\"u1dcd5a25\">方向性的流动感</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u19a9a867\" id=\"u19a9a867\">，就像极光带或者被拉伸的光影。它们通常在水平或对角线方向上延伸。</span></p><ul list=\"u765e1ec0\"><li fid=\"uc4e56271\" data-lake-id=\"uef713f80\" id=\"uef713f80\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1a3c08e8\" id=\"u1a3c08e8\">视觉特征：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u183dbc8d\" id=\"u183dbc8d\"> 被拉伸的长条形、有明显的流动方向、色彩带状融合。</span></li><li fid=\"uc4e56271\" data-lake-id=\"u7b3203c9\" id=\"u7b3203c9\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u10cd2533\" id=\"u10cd2533\">适用场景：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u66a28eed\" id=\"u66a28eed\"> 强调速度感、科技感的产品，或者作为分割线背景。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id=\"12839643-1\" id=\"12839643-1\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua9655506\" id=\"ua9655506\">Vibe Coding 指南：</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u1794ec08\" id=\"u1794ec08\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucb7d878a\" id=\"ucb7d878a\">这个类型的关键是**“拉伸”</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud8af3f5e\" id=\"ud8af3f5e\">和</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0c434532\" id=\"u0c434532\">“变形”**。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc7d71beb\" id=\"uc7d71beb\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud3616bd2\" id=\"ud3616bd2\">Prompt 策略：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1b020b58\" id=\"u1b020b58\"> 不要让 AI 画圆，让它画“长条”，并使用 CSS 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uadef2a5f\" id=\"uadef2a5f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u58e6957f\" id=\"u58e6957f\">transform</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4c382650\" id=\"u4c382650\"> 属性进行倾斜或旋转，制造动势。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf39e95bb\" id=\"uf39e95bb\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5ff2a84f\" id=\"u5ff2a84f\">实操 Vibe Prompt:</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc02de168\" id=\"uc02de168\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0be8555e\" id=\"u0be8555e\">&quot;Create a modern 'aurora light' effect flowing diagonally across the middle of the screen.</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u54dd27e9\" id=\"u54dd27e9\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u08272c2d\" id=\"u08272c2d\">How to vibe it:</span></strong></p><ol list=\"u2a8ef700\"><li fid=\"u4f4966cf\" data-lake-id=\"u9d7e79b9\" id=\"u9d7e79b9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8bac2a42\" id=\"u8bac2a42\">Create a wide, elongated container placed absolutely behind the text section.</span></li><li fid=\"u4f4966cf\" data-lake-id=\"u75b1c3f7\" id=\"u75b1c3f7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3c99da0f\" id=\"u3c99da0f\">Inside, add 2-3 wide, horizontal gradient bars.</span></li><li fid=\"u4f4966cf\" data-lake-id=\"u148d9a62\" id=\"u148d9a62\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubbcc723c\" id=\"ubbcc723c\">Key Step:</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u99079c24\" id=\"u99079c24\"> Rotate and skew the container (e.g., </span><code data-lake-id=\"u6ff09cb1\" id=\"u6ff09cb1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2cd13b2e\" id=\"u2cd13b2e\">rotate-12 scale-x-150</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u230ce71d\" id=\"u230ce71d\">) to create a stretched, flowing sense of movement.</span></li><li fid=\"u4f4966cf\" data-lake-id=\"udfe7cce4\" id=\"udfe7cce4\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud9f82415\" id=\"ud9f82415\">Apply heavy blur to make the light streaks blend smoothly, looking like liquid light.&quot;</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"u14820e0d\" id=\"u14820e0d\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5933c07a\" id=\"u5933c07a\">设计师暗语（Vibe Check）：</span></strong></p><ul list=\"u84f7ac7d\"><li fid=\"uff13bf15\" data-lake-id=\"u69b06009\" id=\"u69b06009\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud1f9853f\" id=\"ud1f9853f\">如果太生硬，就喊：&quot;Stretch it more! Make it look like light streaks.&quot; (再拉伸一点，让它像光束)</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"uad22984b\" id=\"uad22984b\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1769333416903-4331f6da-6990-4ad5-924d-e014fed38e23.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u3b7e8290-16c4-4510-a2b0-4f2cf041ae1%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uf66420f0-73bc-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A1099%2C%22height%22%3A646%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2026-01-25%2017.30.00.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A761066%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A2198%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1292%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22NEW%20EFFECT%20LIQUIDLIGHT%20A%20MODERN%20BACKGROUND%20TECHNIQUE%20USING%20HEAVY%20BLURS%2CROTATION%2C%20AND%20GRADIENTS%20TO%20SIMULATE%20AN%20AURORA%20BOREALIS%20EFFECT.%20GET%20STARTED%20VIEW%20DOCUMENTATION%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A1000%2C%22y%22%3A331%2C%22width%22%3A191%2C%22height%22%3A26%2C%22text%22%3A%22NEW%20EFFECT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A617%2C%22y%22%3A421%2C%22width%22%3A974%2C%22height%22%3A199%2C%22text%22%3A%22LIQUIDLIGHT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A446%2C%22y%22%3A689%2C%22width%22%3A1306%2C%22height%22%3A41%2C%22text%22%3A%22A%20MODERN%20BACKGROUND%20TECHNIQUE%20USING%20HEAVY%20BLURS%2CROTATION%2C%20AND%20GRADIENTS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A785%2C%22y%22%3A751%2C%22width%22%3A631%2C%22height%22%3A35%2C%22text%22%3A%22TO%20SIMULATE%20AN%20AURORA%20BOREALIS%20EFFECT.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A772%2C%22y%22%3A915%2C%22width%22%3A184%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22GET%20STARTED%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1113%2C%22y%22%3A915%2C%22width%22%3A311%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22VIEW%20DOCUMENTATION%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23233461%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u90dbad58%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua7c7e83c\" id=\"ua7c7e83c\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaccc872e\" id=\"uaccc872e\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud20748d8\" id=\"ud20748d8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9134e516\" id=\"u9134e516\">​</span><br></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22dcqUe%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"3e08ef94\" id=\"3e08ef94\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7042db21\" id=\"u7042db21\">类型三：高光聚焦/卡片光晕 (The Focal Glow)</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ud8731a1c\" id=\"ud8731a1c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7dd6e786\" id=\"u7dd6e786\">这种类型不是为了做背景，而是为了</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2f7c9fc0\" id=\"u2f7c9fc0\">突出前景的某个元素</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9a37e563\" id=\"u9a37e563\">。它就像在卡片、图片或按钮后面打了一盏柔光灯，让主体“浮”起来。</span></p><ul list=\"uc2f03114\"><li fid=\"u97409ba9\" data-lake-id=\"ud5dcbda7\" id=\"ud5dcbda7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf42c54a3\" id=\"uf42c54a3\">视觉特征：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua2d8c6ac\" id=\"ua2d8c6ac\"> 范围小、位置精确在主体后方、颜色通常与主体互补或呼应。</span></li><li fid=\"u97409ba9\" data-lake-id=\"uecbadbdf\" id=\"uecbadbdf\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8adee36b\" id=\"u8adee36b\">适用场景：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u01d17d26\" id=\"u01d17d26\"> 强调关键数据卡片、NFT展示、主要 CTA 按钮。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id=\"12839643-2\" id=\"12839643-2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u59cb40ff\" id=\"u59cb40ff\">Vibe Coding 指南：</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u9977ca2f\" id=\"u9977ca2f\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua8867129\" id=\"ua8867129\">这个类型的关键是**“层级关系”</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u513513b4\" id=\"u513513b4\">和</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u91c95984\" id=\"u91c95984\">“约束”**。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u129e6444\" id=\"u129e6444\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u76516a72\" id=\"u76516a72\">Prompt 策略：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3450f48c\" id=\"u3450f48c\"> 必须明确告诉 AI 父子容器关系，一定要用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9ec3ae39\" id=\"u9ec3ae39\"><span data-lake-id=\"u91c285fb\" id=\"u91c285fb\">absolute</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4130d932\" id=\"u4130d932\"> 定位在组件内部，并且常常需要 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3a908945\" id=\"u3a908945\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue1e121f6\" id=\"ue1e121f6\">overflow-hidden</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u96104543\" id=\"u96104543\"> 来把光晕限制在卡片内。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2813174f\" id=\"u2813174f\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubf87d718\" id=\"ubf87d718\">实操 Vibe Prompt:</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf5089383\" id=\"uf5089383\"><span data-lake-id=\"uabf4234b\" id=\"uabf4234b\">&quot;I want to make this feature card pop with a subtle 'glow effect' behind the icon.</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2cbb2352\" id=\"u2cbb2352\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u710ff059\" id=\"u710ff059\">Instructions:</span></strong></p><ol list=\"u9190c965\"><li fid=\"ue252bb60\" data-lake-id=\"u05f56c40\" id=\"u05f56c40\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubdde593e\" id=\"ubdde593e\">Make sure the card container is set to </span><code data-lake-id=\"ude2dbe17\" id=\"ude2dbe17\"><span data-lake-id=\"u84c0bcd2\" id=\"u84c0bcd2\">relative</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf1ecd8f7\" id=\"uf1ecd8f7\"> and </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua2cfadb6\" id=\"ua2cfadb6\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaa72b627\" id=\"uaa72b627\">overflow-hidden</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4bc4bf74\" id=\"u4bc4bf74\">.</span></li><li fid=\"ue252bb60\" data-lake-id=\"ua738a14b\" id=\"ua738a14b\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf548743d\" id=\"uf548743d\">Add a colored blob (e.g., brand primary color) inside the card, absolutely positioned right behind the main icon/image.</span></li><li fid=\"ue252bb60\" data-lake-id=\"u8735f3a6\" id=\"u8735f3a6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u02c5ceb7\" id=\"u02c5ceb7\">Apply heavy blur and reduce opacity.</span></li><li fid=\"ue252bb60\" data-lake-id=\"u33d72878\" id=\"u33d72878\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5aba4ebb\" id=\"u5aba4ebb\">The result should look like a soft light source emerging from behind the icon, contained within the card boundaries.&quot;</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"ubb1562c2\" id=\"ubb1562c2\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1a5daa26\" id=\"u1a5daa26\">设计师暗语（Vibe Check）：</span></strong></p><ul list=\"ubb21725a\"><li fid=\"u0b7acb46\" data-lake-id=\"u1bcb8934\" id=\"u1bcb8934\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9149c209\" id=\"u9149c209\">如果光溢出来了，就喊：&quot;The glow is leaking outside the card. Add </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3fd8436b\" id=\"u3fd8436b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u76175ee3\" id=\"u76175ee3\">overflow-hidden</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue6daacc0\" id=\"ue6daacc0\"> to the container.&quot;</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u27bee858\" id=\"u27bee858\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1769333524768-71983bb5-8065-4a00-94f3-c203f149dc56.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u621465d5-c64c-4718-80f8-5a1a7910e4a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uf66420f0-73bc-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A965%2C%22height%22%3A427%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2026-01-25%2017.31.47.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A290788%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1930%2C%22originHeight%22%3A854%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22LIGHTNING%20FAST%20MAGICAL%20AI%20AUTOMATE%20YOUR%20WORKFLOW%20WITH%20INTELLIGENT%20AGENTS.%20OUR%20INFRASTRUCTURE%20IS%20OPTIMIZED%20FOR%20SPEED.THE%20NOTICE%20HOW%20THE%20'OVERFLOW-HIDDEN%20ON%20THE%20PARENT%20GLOW%20BEHIND%20THE%20ICON%20CREATES%20A%20FOCAL%20POINT%20THAT%20CONTAINER%20CUTS%20OFF%20THE%20GLOW%20CLEANLY%20AT%20THE%20EDGES.%20DRAWS%20THE%20USER'S%20EYE%20IMMEDIATELY%20TO%20THE%20FEATURE'S%20PURPOSE.%20EXPLORE%20TOOLS%20LEARN%20MORE%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A132%2C%22y%22%3A308%2C%22width%22%3A283%2C%22height%22%3A46%2C%22text%22%3A%22LIGHTNING%20FAST%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1059%2C%22y%22%3A308%2C%22width%22%3A210%2C%22height%22%3A41%2C%22text%22%3A%22MAGICAL%20AI%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1061%2C%22y%22%3A391%2C%22width%22%3A718%2C%22height%22%3A33%2C%22text%22%3A%22AUTOMATE%20YOUR%20WORKFLOW%20WITH%20INTELLIGENT%20AGENTS.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A135%2C%22y%22%3A389%2C%22width%22%3A692%2C%22height%22%3A36%2C%22text%22%3A%22OUR%20INFRASTRUCTURE%20IS%20OPTIMIZED%20FOR%20SPEED.THE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1060%2C%22y%22%3A442%2C%22width%22%3A723%2C%22height%22%3A33%2C%22text%22%3A%22NOTICE%20HOW%20THE%20'OVERFLOW-HIDDEN%20ON%20THE%20PARENT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A133%2C%22y%22%3A444%2C%22width%22%3A701%2C%22height%22%3A34%2C%22text%22%3A%22GLOW%20BEHIND%20THE%20ICON%20CREATES%20A%20FOCAL%20POINT%20THAT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1061%2C%22y%22%3A494%2C%22width%22%3A729%2C%22height%22%3A36%2C%22text%22%3A%22CONTAINER%20CUTS%20OFF%20THE%20GLOW%20CLEANLY%20AT%20THE%20EDGES.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A134%2C%22y%22%3A495%2C%22width%22%3A604%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22DRAWS%20THE%20USER'S%20EYE%20IMMEDIATELY%20TO%20THE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A131%2C%22y%22%3A548%2C%22width%22%3A279%2C%22height%22%3A30%2C%22text%22%3A%22FEATURE'S%20PURPOSE.%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1059%2C%22y%22%3A594%2C%22width%22%3A181%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22EXPLORE%20TOOLS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A132%2C%22y%22%3A650%2C%22width%22%3A158%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22LEARN%20MORE%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%230d1123%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ud6432385%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22Uk7sJ%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"93e6587a\" id=\"93e6587a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3b6b72fd\" id=\"u3b6b72fd\">类型四：呼吸动态弥散 (The Animated Gradient)</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"uc745dbb3\" id=\"uc745dbb3\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue55f19be\" id=\"ue55f19be\">这是最高级的一种形式。弥散的光斑不再是静止的，而是缓慢地移动、变形、忽明忽暗，仿佛有生命力一般。</span></p><ul list=\"u33ef60b5\"><li fid=\"u4ecc06d6\" data-lake-id=\"u1a883bad\" id=\"u1a883bad\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud5107cf5\" id=\"ud5107cf5\">视觉特征：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc638a119\" id=\"uc638a119\"> 缓慢移动、变形、颜色循环流动、非常微妙。</span></li><li fid=\"u4ecc06d6\" data-lake-id=\"ud9c5e637\" id=\"ud9c5e637\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u74679bd2\" id=\"u74679bd2\">适用场景：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u89a73bcd\" id=\"u89a73bcd\"> 想要极致高级感和生命力的 Hero Section。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id=\"12839643-3\" id=\"12839643-3\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucb5e3f95\" id=\"ucb5e3f95\">Vibe Coding 指南：</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u3b4d6ae2\" id=\"u3b4d6ae2\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaeab7e54\" id=\"uaeab7e54\">这个类型的关键是“慢”</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua8fe5ccd\" id=\"ua8fe5ccd\">和</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue1f430f2\" id=\"ue1f430f2\">“微妙”。切忌快速闪烁。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufd060ffa\" id=\"ufd060ffa\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc124d6be\" id=\"uc124d6be\">Prompt 策略：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7cdea6a0\" id=\"u7cdea6a0\"> 在基础的“色块+模糊”基础上，指挥 AI 添加 CSS Animation。重点是描述动画的感觉。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u36f72e7b\" id=\"u36f72e7b\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5939a594\" id=\"u5939a594\">实操 Vibe Prompt:</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"uea19d7bc\" id=\"uea19d7bc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5caed274\" id=\"u5caed274\">&quot;Take the diffuse background blobs you just created, and bring them to life with subtle animation.</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3a2c11aa\" id=\"u3a2c11aa\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua1e40cba\" id=\"ua1e40cba\">Vibe requirement:</span></strong></p><ol list=\"uac082122\"><li fid=\"u45283af2\" data-lake-id=\"u70a5e3cb\" id=\"u70a5e3cb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6b3e0acd\" id=\"u6b3e0acd\">Add a slow, infinite CSS animation to each blob.</span></li><li fid=\"u45283af2\" data-lake-id=\"u43b5affa\" id=\"u43b5affa\"><span data-lake-id=\"u282b359e\" id=\"u282b359e\">They should gently float around, changing their position and scale over a long duration (e.g., 2s or 3s cycle).</span></li><li fid=\"u45283af2\" data-lake-id=\"u33850b90\" id=\"u33850b90\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udb865d72\" id=\"udb865d72\">Crucial:</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uae10b43d\" id=\"uae10b43d\"> The movement must be very slow, subtle, and fluid, like lava lamp wax or breathing. Do NOT make it fast or chaotic.&quot;</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"u9651f0e4\" id=\"u9651f0e4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uffe9c31f\" id=\"uffe9c31f\">设计师暗语（Vibe Check）：</span></strong></p><ul list=\"u3342bbb9\"><li fid=\"u49295aed\" data-lake-id=\"u3bdead5f\" id=\"u3bdead5f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2b2a1a82\" id=\"u2b2a1a82\">如果动得太快，就喊：&quot;Too fast! Make it 10x slower. It should be barely noticeable, like breathing.&quot; (太快了！慢 10 倍。要几乎察觉不到，像呼吸一样)</span></li></ul><card type=\"block\" name=\"video\" value=\"data:%7B%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E6%B8%90%E5%8F%98.mov%22%2C%22size%22%3A29177173%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub30c46be-ca57-4a0c-b75a-69357abf7de%22%2C%22taskType%22%3A%22upload%22%2C%22url%22%3Anull%2C%22cover%22%3Anull%2C%22videoId%22%3A%22inputs%2Fprod%2Fyuque%2F2026%2F1206632%2Fmov%2F1769335789467-062c6dfa-8e7b-42bb-8c27-ba60c0761569.mov%22%2C%22download%22%3Afalse%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22HQm8h%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"ua409caba\" id=\"ua409caba\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf763219e\" id=\"uf763219e\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue580537e\" id=\"ue580537e\"><br></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22VNZg7%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"25f9c7fa\" id=\"25f9c7fa\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1804457b\" id=\"u1804457b\">总结</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ud99013db\" id=\"ud99013db\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaec13f63\" id=\"uaec13f63\">Vibe Coding 弥散渐变，本质上是在用自然语言指挥 AI 进行一场“光影魔术”。</span></p><ul list=\"u66a2b09e\"><li fid=\"ub65957ec\" data-lake-id=\"u8a10d5a2\" id=\"u8a10d5a2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0de0e8d8\" id=\"u0de0e8d8\">想要氛围？做</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1360686b\" id=\"u1360686b\">大背景</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u159f4363\" id=\"u159f4363\">，关键词是“huge blobs, extreme blur”。</span></li><li fid=\"ub65957ec\" data-lake-id=\"u2153ddc5\" id=\"u2153ddc5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u334093e1\" id=\"u334093e1\">想要动势？做</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1d580ec8\" id=\"u1d580ec8\">极光</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u189e4e27\" id=\"u189e4e27\">，关键词是“stretched, rotated, light streaks”。</span></li><li fid=\"ub65957ec\" data-lake-id=\"u84f130a1\" id=\"u84f130a1\"><span data-lake-id=\"udadc7d9c\" id=\"udadc7d9c\">想要聚焦？做</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9660cae1\" id=\"u9660cae1\">光晕</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf319c7a8\" id=\"uf319c7a8\">，关键词是“behind element, contained glow”。</span></li><li fid=\"ub65957ec\" data-lake-id=\"uc5118a0e\" id=\"uc5118a0e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u422677dc\" id=\"u422677dc\">想要生命力？加</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7aae18b9\" id=\"u7aae18b9\">动画</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubbe68e1a\" id=\"ubbe68e1a\">，关键词是“slow, subtle floating animation”。</span></li></ul>"}
